    "A signal can be considered useful if it produces a competitive or higher Sharpe ratio than buy-and-hold, or if it achieves a similar Sharpe ratio with lower drawdowns. Differences across stocks are expected because Apple, Nvidia and Mercedes-Benz have different volatility profiles, sector exposures and trend behavior."
